            <description><![CDATA[【🙊<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%82%9D%E4%B8%8D%E5%A5%BD%E8%BA%AB%E4%BD%93%E4%BC%9A%E5%8F%98%E8%87%AD%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%82%9D%E4%B8%8D%E5%A5%BD%E8%BA%AB%E4%BD%93%E4%BC%9A%E5%8F%98%E8%87%AD%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#肝不好身体会变臭#</span></a>？】天天熬夜，过量饮酒，容易生病……这些不良习惯可能正在损害你的肝！非酒精性脂肪肝是我国发病率最高的慢性肝病，平均每4个人中就会有1人患病。脂肪肝离肝癌只有4步？体检时要注意肝脏哪些指标？什么运动适合脂肪肝患者？脂肪肝可逆吗？今天，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%85%A8%E5%9B%BD%E7%88%B1%E8%82%9D%E6%97%A5%23&amp;isnewpage=1" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#全国爱肝日#</span></a>，请善待你的肝<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[爱你]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_aini-09d5f3f870.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>（央视网）<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hnuxwmh19oj20u0140k2k.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hnuxwmvpwcj20u01407fx.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hnuxwm5xosj20u0140n84.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hnuxwmbx7gj20u0140drb.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hnuxwmcj2oj20u0140dqu.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hnuxwm1e32j20u0140n9f.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hnuxwko991j20u0140k28.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="http